{"tid":148064,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[狗鐵]撞左個阿嬸好L爽","createTime":"2017-03-08T10:11:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-08T21:45:10.000Z","uid":62868,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"51dff781a687d610109ef236f18238e1f1f2efd7","tid":148064,"uid":62868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T10:11:08.000Z","msg":"岩岩搭狗鐵係總站落車 成班人逼上黎 中間留番既位連隻狗都未必夠位出<br />\n<br />\n跟住我落車個陣用膊頭好似玩美式足球咁用膊頭撞兩邊既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n撞到有個阿嬸失平衡跌一跌 感覺好爽 佢淨係啤左我一眼 zip左我一zip<br />\n<br />\n總站都要逼上車 驚鬼死冇得上車咩 逼上車鬥快搵位坐 食屎 落地獄啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇人有類似既經歷?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98df30f1197e2a71d56aae7f0dea40484b2a6981","tid":148064,"uid":21664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T10:11:55.000Z","msg":"好有畫面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f91b1ebbbca56cbff62ec344e0221176e59fa279","tid":148064,"uid":62868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T10:13:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好有畫面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打係咪好有同感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets