心."},{"pid":"88525c97cd062ef5917a9886a8cd5304fcd0bfe1","tid":148064,"uid":62868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T20:19:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>地鐵真係日日都遇到這類人啦<br />\n<br />\n有次有兩隻蝗婆 (好高大) 一手掃開個女人落車<br />\n掃到個女人撞埋塊玻璃度<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n掃著隻亦係蝗<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港人口已經係以中国人蝗蟲為主, 見到都唔開心.</blockquote><br />\n每日有成150個人黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但點解你知佢地係蝗既?"},{"pid":"4a9b2023fe4653a68f30c3e94dddb341b598ec33","tid":148064,"uid":20658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T21:45:10.000Z","msg":"有次有條傻西專登撞9我，即刻開佢波，佢say晒sorry dup底個頭咁走"}]}